SELECT TOP(1) [order].[Id], [order].[CreatedAt], [order].[Email], [order].[EndDate], [order].[Name], [order].[OrderNumber], [order].[StartDate], [order].[Status], [order].[UniversityId]
FROM [Orders] AS [order]
WHERE [order].[Id] = @__id_0
ORDER BY [order].[Id]
2019-09-21 16:58:46.164 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [order.Products].[Id], [order.Products].[OrderId], [order.Products].[ProductId], [order.Products].[Quantity], [order.Products].[UnitPrice], [o.Product].[Id], [o.Product].[CreatedAt], [o.Product].[Description], [o.Product].[Image], [o.Product].[Name], [o.Product].[Price]
FROM [OrderItem] AS [order.Products]
LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [o.Product] ON [order.Products].[ProductId] = [o.Product].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT TOP(1) [order0].[Id]
    FROM [Orders] AS [order0]
    WHERE [order0].[Id] = @__id_0
    ORDER BY [order0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [order.Products].[OrderId] = [t].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]
2019-09-21 16:58:46.167 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@p8='?' (DbType = Guid), @p0='?' (DbType = DateTimeOffset), @p1='?' (Size = 4000), @p2='?' (DbType = DateTimeOffset), @p3='?' (Size = 4000), @p4='?' (Size = 4000), @p5='?' (DbType = DateTimeOffset), @p6='?' (DbType = Int32), @p7='?' (Size = 4000)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SET NOCOUNT ON;
UPDATE [Orders] SET [CreatedAt] = @p0, [Email] = @p1, [EndDate] = @p2, [Name] = @p3, [OrderNumber] = @p4, [StartDate] = @p5, [Status] = @p6, [UniversityId] = @p7

FROM [OrderItem] AS [order.Products]
LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [o.Product] ON [order.Products].[ProductId] = [o.Product].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT TOP(1) [order0].[Id]
    FROM [Orders] AS [order0]
    WHERE [order0].[Id] = @__id_0
    ORDER BY [order0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [order.Products].[OrderId] = [t].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]

ORDER BY [order].[Id]
2019-09-22 20:54:48.085 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (63ms) [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [order.Products].[Id], [order.Products].[OrderId], [order.Products].[ProductId], [order.Products].[Quantity], [order.Products].[UnitPrice], [o.Product].[Id], [o.Product].[CreatedAt], [o.Product].[Description], [o.Product].[Image], [o.Product].[Name], [o.Product].[Price]
FROM [OrderItem] AS [order.Products]
LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [o.Product] ON [order.Products].[ProductId] = [o.Product].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT TOP(1) [order0].[Id]
    FROM [Orders] AS [order0]
    WHERE [order0].[Id] = @__id_0
    ORDER BY [order0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [order.Products].[OrderId] = [t].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]
